text: John Moylan (born 11 January 1953) is a former Australian rules footballer who played with North Melbourne and Footscray in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * * Category:Living people Category:1953 births Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:North Melbourne Football Club players Category:Western Bulldogs players Category:University Blues Football Club players
